### Test Redis Caching trong API Gateway

### ========================================
### BƯỚC 1: Lấy JWT Token
### ========================================

### 1.1. Generate Token
POST http://localhost:5050/auth/generate-token
Content-Type: application/json
ClientId: cache-test

{
  "username": "testuser"
}

### ========================================
### BƯỚC 2: Test Caching cho Pricing GET
### ========================================
### Cache TTL: 30 giây, Region: "pricing"

### 2.1. First Request - Sẽ hit downstream service
GET http://localhost:5050/pricing
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
ClientId: cache-test-pricing

### 2.2. Second Request - Sẽ trả về từ Redis cache (nhanh hơn)
GET http://localhost:5050/pricing
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
ClientId: cache-test-pricing

### 2.3. Third Request - Vẫn từ cache
GET http://localhost:5050/pricing
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
ClientId: cache-test-pricing

### ========================================
### BƯỚC 3: Test Caching cho Pricing GET by ID
### ========================================
### Cache TTL: 60 giây, Region: "pricing-details"

### 3.1. First Request for ID 123 - Hit downstream
GET http://localhost:5050/pricing/123
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
ClientId: cache-test-details

### 3.2. Second Request for ID 123 - From cache
GET http://localhost:5050/pricing/123
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
ClientId: cache-test-details

### 3.3. Request for different ID 456 - Hit downstream (different cache key)
GET http://localhost:5050/pricing/456
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
ClientId: cache-test-details

### 3.4. Second Request for ID 456 - From cache
GET http://localhost:5050/pricing/456
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
ClientId: cache-test-details

### ========================================
### BƯỚC 4: Test Caching cho Policy
### ========================================
### Cache TTL: 120 giây (2 phút), Region: "policy"

### 4.1. First Request - Hit downstream
GET http://localhost:5050/policy
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
ClientId: cache-test-policy

### 4.2. Second Request - From cache
GET http://localhost:5050/policy
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
ClientId: cache-test-policy

### ========================================
### BƯỚC 5: Test Cache Headers
### ========================================
### Kiểm tra response headers để xác nhận caching

### 5.1. Request với verbose headers
GET http://localhost:5050/pricing
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
ClientId: cache-headers-test

### ========================================
### EXPECTED RESULTS
### ========================================
### - First requests: Slower response time (hit downstream)
### - Subsequent requests: Faster response time (from Redis cache)
### - Different cache regions for different endpoints
### - Cache TTL: Pricing (30s), Pricing Details (60s), Policy (120s)
### - Cache keys include route parameters (e.g., pricing/123 vs pricing/456)